{"tid":272917,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳豬：我是支那人！","createTime":"2017-06-06T07:26:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-06T09:57:34.000Z","uid":20241,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"52f430f275da310e3fa3b64a033f64814397994b","tid":272917,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T07:26:01.000Z","msg":"72%學生：我是中國人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n    國民身份認同感較上次調查大幅提升<br />\n<br />\n    72%學生：我是中國人<br />\n<br />\n    【本報消息】團體調查發現，本澳年輕一代的國民身份認同感提升。肯定自己是&ldquo;中國人&rdquo;的中學生增至七成二，較一四年增加一成七，超過六成中學生感到中國人的身份很重要。研究者認為，數據與中國政治、經濟良性發展有關。<br />\n<br />\n    具較強公民責任感<br />\n<br />\n    學聯和青年研究協會曾於○七、○九、一一和一四年開展本澳中學生國民身份認同調查，今年再發佈報告。調查於四月十七日至五月二日在十五所學校以不記名問卷方式進行，回收有效問卷一千二百多份。受訪者中，內地出生的佔兩成八，較歷次調查明顯升高（一四年逾一成八、○九年逾一成五）。研究人員分析，可能是回歸後的投資移民政策，使內地的新移民增多，其中部分人攜幼年子女移居本澳，當前正處於中學時期。<br />\n<br />\n    調查發現中學生的國民身份認同感提升，七成二受訪者肯定自己是&ldquo;中國人&rdquo;，較一四年的五成半有較大回升。對&ldquo;中國人身份對自己來說很重要&rdquo;的表述持肯定態度的中學生，一四年不足四成，這次回升至六成多。學生亦表現出較強的公民責任感，近七成表示會在將來行使投票權，與一四年數據持平。<br />\n<br />\n    多藉學校認識祖國<br />\n<br />\n    中學生認識祖國的首要途徑亦有改變，&ldquo;課堂／書本&rdquo;由一四年的百分之三十二點四提高至百分之六十點六，超過&ldquo;互聯網&rdquo;躍居第一，第二至六位依次為互聯網（百分之五十九點七）、到內地探視／旅遊、報章／雜誌、與親朋好友交流、參加赴內地的交流活動。<br />\n<br />\n    學生關注澳門新聞較高，四成表示非常關心，三成半&ldquo;會關心&rdquo;；關注中國新聞較一四年僅提升兩成，三成多稱非常關心，三成半&ldquo;會關心&rdquo;。學生對時事有一定關注，譬如關於中國政府在危急時刻海外撤僑的態度，五成人認為&ldquo;應該的，較為讚賞&rdquo;，三成人認為&ldquo;非常讚賞，非常自豪&rdquo;，表示不關心或者不知道的分別佔兩成。<br />\n<br />\n    國家政經發展有關<br />\n<br />\n    研究者分析，一四年澳門中學生對中國人身份的認同感降低的原因，與受當時香港等周邊局勢以及內地貪腐等負面新聞影響有關。是次認同感回升，與近年中國政治、經濟良性發展，國家實力日益強大和國際地位提升，以及近年努力推進&ldquo;一國兩制&rdquo;事業、維護澳門繁榮穩定與國民教育工作密不可分，但香港、台灣等周邊地區以及部分國際局勢的負面影響依然存在。[img]<a href=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/06/152536_6c475ab80acb647892e19fe2270f6433.jpg[/img］\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F06%2F152536_6c475ab80acb647892e19fe2270f6433.jpg%5B%2Fimg%EF%BC%BD&d=KAzopUd0ERei3WjkYpC2Txxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=d42a54b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/06/152536_6c475ab80acb647892e19fe2270f6433.jpg[/img］</a>"},{"pid":"46f4c964c57dd1448bb8032860b75b7357f53a6a","tid":272917,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T07:27:54.000Z","msg":"補圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/06/152745_b87723d5cfbfd50ee6a32fdf691968a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F06%2F152745_b87723d5cfbfd50ee6a32fdf691968a1.jpg&h=085ab358&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5f72a0b7d2d0ea3b2b25dbf93021aa92852c0ecd","tid":272917,"uid":22858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T07:31:47.000Z","msg":"垃圾地方 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3967dd93093155c32327a4c6b983813cc8c4bd4b","tid":272917,"uid":1865,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T07:34:29.000Z","msg":"唔講真係唔記得呢個地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n旅行個陣班撚樣咪又係爭住認香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n行撚開啦澳狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ddafd91807b63453ed2664054935a4536b93239","tid":272917,"uid":93784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T07:41:30.000Z","msg":"當中佔左幾多成係支那移民?"},{"pid":"d4228337505d56d423675abbeac5404aa91720b3","tid":272917,"uid":34184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T07:44:23.000Z","msg":"記名調查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23d12ac60184bb6ce7acea036fa3273631acaa59","tid":272917,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T07:46:14.000Z","msg":"大佬啊，年年咁派錢，十年成十皮啊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fa4819d9aeaab26462149db018b61e69f6a6d0b","tid":272917,"uid":53731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T07:50:35.000Z","msg":"學校由細開始教佢地認做中國人，中學雞點會識分。"},{"pid":"f80da7dd51f496c532d79b75ed3fda23f00cb346","tid":272917,"uid":50660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T07:50:54.000Z","msg":"你睇澳門幾乖 抵佢地年年有錢派<br />\n<br />\n香港人唔該乖d認自己做支那人咪大家開開心心生活囉，對不對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4df9269489c3254bae8d1eb454549586c12c8637","tid":272917,"uid":42872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T07:52:43.000Z","msg":"澳門日報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecfc4f8c84fb3085e66d9b89c32d4f57bba8cf2d","tid":272917,"uid":48,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T07:53:21.000Z","msg":"之前葡國搞到澳門一pat屎<br />\n<br />\n同英國管治既香港差太遠"},{"pid":"3831caadc99b3caed9ff0f6b34c3f4abfbe0fb20","tid":272917,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T07:53:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"700b9309ac4d15470facb6c4b8e01d100dd7c67e","tid":272917,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T07:56:08.000Z","msg":"4分一人都係大陸出世，同有大陸人有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bcbb1fb21caaf6580e11808133549eadb68e822","tid":272917,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T08:10:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/paper/685783\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fpaper%2F685783&d=KAzopUd0ERei3WjkYpC2Txxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=4f5d7ac5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fpaper%2F685783&h=592d5922\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/paper/685783</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mingpaocanada.com/Tor/ftp/News/20150202/HK/_02GC001_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2FTor%2Fftp%2FNews%2F20150202%2FHK%2F_02GC001_.jpg&h=6eced3ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">18歲以上港生 無人自認是中國人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n〔編譯管淑平／綜合報導〕根據香港多份最新民調，港人對中國政府的反感程度，從去年十一月迄今驟升十二個百分點，創下一九九七年「回歸」以來新高。同時，年輕族群只有四％自認是「中國人」，十八歲以上受訪學生甚至無人認同中國人身分。香港特首梁振英的滿意度和支持度也都再創新低。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">港人對中反感 回歸後新高</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n香港大學五月間所做民調顯示，港人對中國政府的反感程度，從去年十一月的二十五％大增到三十七％，好感度則從二十九％降到二十％；調查還發現，三十六％受訪民眾對中國民眾反感的程度，比半年前增加一成。港大民意研究計畫總監鍾庭耀指出，港人對中國民眾的反感度劇增，反映中港兩地生活文化的矛盾，必須予以正視。<br />\n<br />\n在身分認同方面，香港浸會大學的「香港過渡期研究計畫」訪問九百多名香港民眾的最新民調中，四成受訪者認同自己是「中國人」，自認是「香港中國人」、「香港人」的比率各為二十七％和十七％。然而，在十八到二十九歲的年輕族群中，只有四％自認是「中國人」，其中十八歲以上受訪學生所佔比率更是零。負責這項調查的浸會大學教授戴高禮認為，這與被視為洗腦的國民教育風波有關。<br />\n<br />\n中文大學政治與行政學系高級講師蔡子強指出，中共領導人換屆，一度令人期待在提升人權、解決貪腐等方面有所作為，但中共總書記、國家主席習近平上任半年來，政治及人權情況並未改善，又再傳官員貪腐，港人對中央政府反感程度自然上升。<br />\n<br />\n浸會大學這份民調還顯示，香港公務員不滿政府的比率最高，六十二％不滿和非常不滿政府表現，七十六％認為政府施政不公平和非常不公平；民間機構人員這兩者的比率各為五十六％和六十五％。<br />\n<br />\n此外，中文大學香港亞太研究所五月底訪問七百多名香港市民，民眾對梁振英的表現評分從前一個月的四十九．三分，跌到四十六分，創下他上任七個月以來新低點，也是連六個月不及格。梁振英聲望持續探底，據信與其政府上任後醜聞不斷、弊案頻傳有關。"},{"pid":"4e7d5df1b15c8cbc43c9f7e5c4d600db809b2b43","tid":272917,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T08:14:45.000Z","msg":"做個勇敢中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b97f7a3b576065b1b3031cf857892551caef747","tid":272917,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T08:16:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做個勇敢中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n居港支那人大集會：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20170604/_2017060420264210215.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20170604%2F_2017060420264210215.jpg&h=e2f9c25d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca532d3fce649e535b246c1ed393f4884a508772","tid":272917,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T08:21:24.000Z","msg":"年年派9000蚊,認習近平係我契爺都仲得"},{"pid":"c93cb6d65802cef01b4763fd6f0ad16f50bdd403","tid":272917,"uid":27120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T08:28:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前葡國搞到澳門一pat屎<br />\n<br />\n同英國管治既香港差太遠</blockquote><br />\n好似六七暴動之前都唔係咁好<br />\n但之後英國政府真係有正視到啲問題<br />\n先令到班地下共產黨員發唔到圍<br />\n如果唔係香港一早變到同澳門一樣"},{"pid":"9159bd6e5d58fed82fa531c257ee61e2dd3dc982","tid":272917,"uid":27772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T08:34:42.000Z","msg":"唔好笑 <br />\n香港班00後都唔樂觀 <br />\n最後抗爭的一代可能已經係90後"},{"pid":"d360c45800f07d720d7fdb371ea0939dcb72fc04","tid":272917,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T08:39:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好笑 <br />\n香港班00後都唔樂觀 <br />\n最後抗爭的一代可能已經係90後</blockquote><br />\n最後一屈"},{"pid":"0165b079ef509273789de5edd68f1fb67a4024ed","tid":272917,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T08:41:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好笑 <br />\n香港班00後都唔樂觀 <br />\n最後抗爭的一代可能已經係90後</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最後的香港人"},{"pid":"42f1775dff8955a1927a43835f04c1eddd8c24c2","tid":272917,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T08:42:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3c8227f30fe5e5df858d687ff1ebed40e16af2e","tid":272917,"uid":48735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T08:43:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>之前葡國搞到澳門一pat屎<br />\n<br />\n同英國管治既香港差太遠</blockquote><br />\n好似六七暴動之前都唔係咁好<br />\n但之後英國政府真係有正視到啲問題<br />\n先令到班地下共產黨員發唔到圍<br />\n如果唔係香港一早變到同澳門一樣</blockquote><br />\n當年67暴動前奏<br />\n澳門123事件已經知澳葡幾咁軟弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又要跪又要含共產黨咁"},{"pid":"b18a7b9898192dcb379df505540f34c49a